I"<p>The Liquibase hibernate extension has been updated for both hibernate 3 and hibernate 4.</p>

<p>This release adds support for catching changes to sequences and unique constraints as well as a few bugs around data type handling.</p>

<p>See <a href="https://github.com/liquibase/liquibase-hibernate">https://github.com/liquibase/liquibase-hibernate</a> for more information and to download the 3.1 release.</p>

<p><em>UPDATE:</em>  A null pointer issue was found in the 3.1 release and fixed in a now available 3.2 release.</p>
